00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:32.000
This USB key will work on any of our other rekordbox ready gear as well, we can then load the track and then once we’ve called those cue points they’re all going to be reset from where they’ve been set within rekordbox.

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:38.000
It’s as simple as that you can create them on the R1 or you can create them in rekordbox.

